show.description: When aspiring actress Claire Evens falls into a secret romance with powerful producer Mitch Sterling, her dreams seem within reach—until an unexpected pregnancy turns her world upside down. As Mitch's charm gives way to aggression and ultimatums, Claire finds herself cast out of his life and her hopes shattered. A chance friendship with struggling screenwriter Alex offers a glimmer of support, but Claire's desperate threat to go public with her pregnancy brings Mitch back with newfound warmth. Just as reconciliation seems possible, Claire learns that in Hollywood, second chances often hide the darkest intentions. A haunting tale of ambition, betrayal, and the dangerous price of trust in an industry built on illusions.
